==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quicken tree
<hw>Quick"en tree`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Probably from
<ets>quick</ets>, and first applied to the aspen or some tree with
quivering leaves; cf. G. <ets>quickenbaum</ets>, <ets>quizenbaum</ets>,
<ets>quitschenbaum</ets>. Cf. <er>Quitch grass</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The European rowan tree; -- called also
<altname>quickbeam</altname>, and <altname>quickenbeam</altname>. See
<er>Rowan tree</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>quick-freeze</ent>⟦br⟧
